template
    h2 first step? log in
    form(submit.bind="login()" autocomplete="off")
        text-field(type="text" value.bind="user.username", t="[label]login.username")
        text-field(type="password" value.bind="user.password", t="[label]login.password")
        div.sunshower-button-holder
            button(type="submit")
                | get going
    p if you're not quite there yet,
        | #{' '}
        a(click.delegate="signup()") step zero is to sign up
    p heck, go
        | #{' '}
        a read the docs
        |  -- we'll wait